      'aarti7':"Jaidev Jaidev Jai Mahalingaraya. Bhandar Bhushan Crow's target umbrella shadow.\n\n\nJayadeva, Jayadeva Jayadeva\n\n\nBaramati place is Pattan\nAmrit Bai's youngest child was born to Mahalingaraya . Bhola Shankar, given a boon.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva..1..\n\n\nMahalingarayan suffered a lot.\nSatya's Pandavs go to Koti by toiling for Guru Biroba . After meeting Dharma Raja.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva..2..\n\n\nWith the flowers of the red garden. Bandikhani has been solved by Siddha's Bharuni Pani of\nNagzhari. Pandur Koti left the city.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva 3.\n\n\nBhumi Shirdon is the place of truth. Guru Biroba's abode\nNagzari Shital by bringing flowers. Offering to Guru Biruba.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva ..4..\n\n\nGo to Malappa in Limbal Hills. Taking the tigress's milk,\noffered it to Guru Biroba. Received blessings at Guru's feet.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva..5..\n\n\nNavkhand Prithvi Mahalingaraya. After saving fifty-six countries, she\ngave fortune to the eternal devotee. Came back to Huljanti place.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva .. 6 ..\n\n\nHoma program has been prepared. Brahmashankar Vishnu Murari\nSukshetra Huljanti on the banks of the river. Saints gathered in large numbers.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva ..7..\n\n\nPandharpur Vaikunth Nagar. Shri Pandurang got ready\nand came and saw Huljanti Nagar. Thank you Mahalingarai.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva..8..\n\n\nAt the end of the seven day week. The devotees left with\nKambla sheep donation. A boon given to all Gods.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva..9..\n\n\nMahima Purush Mahaling Bhari. Malappa Birappa on Doolti Chawari\nvillage Huljanti Kailas city. Preparation for Diwali Amavasya Yatra.\n\n\nJaidev. Jayadeva..10..\n\n\nVillage Huljanti Bhuvan Kailas. Poet Adveppa faced\ndifficulties while writing Guruchadhyas Granth. Descendant of Mahalingaraya.\n\n\n.. Jayadeva, Jayadeva, Jayadeva..11..\n\n\nPoet – Sri Adveppa Maharaya",
      'hymn1':"Even if many births go away\nKondyne's place is consumed by Birpati ||\nBirdev avatar revealed for Bhaktodwara daya bira\nnow survara pav majla || Mr ||\n\n\nMatange Bahu spent her childhood with you\nBut you have mercy on him\nThe gracious humble giver salutations to you\nDaya bira now surwara pav floor || 1 ||\n\n\nKolagiri Nagarate Awesome Leela Karuniya |\nChildren play, servants kill Badwonia ||\nSuch was the case that people rushed to fill their lives\nDaya bira now surwara pav floor || 2 ||\n\n\nKarin Meshadi protection for devotees\nDevotees who have completed the body with a lot of hard work\nTishton is pleased with devotion\nDaya bira now surwara pav floor || 3 ||\n\n\nEvil Daityadi Mardoni Bahu protected with saint |\nAdded Kshetra Kodoli for Bhaktodwara ||\nA wonderful majesty was placed behind such a place\nDaya bira now surwara pav floor || 4 ||\n\n\nLila Charitra Narrated Harsh Jhalase Mamachitta |\nGurunatha does not have to describe many things like this\nDas Winvi Birnatha should give inspiration to such a floor |\nDaya bira now surwara pav floor || 5 ||\n\n\n– Mr. Narahari Joshi",
